window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Badgelor has been patient, or at least as patient as a homicidal badger can be. </b></p> <p>With the celebration of Grebthar Day, it's finally time to go get Charles! Nothing is going to stop Jim and his companions, not even the signs of the Dark Overlord's return. This adventure could be Windfall's greatest yet, or it could be its absolute downfall.</p>"; 
